title: Jayonbyolgok
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Buffet and salad bar at 그랜드마트 6층, 노고산동 57-1. Many vegetable side dishes suitable for vegans, including blanched greens, battered fried vegetables and pickles. A separate bibimbap station is entirely vegan (three different varieties of boiled rice with various vegetable toppings and seaweed). Drinks include cinnamon apple punch.
